The Executive Summary provides a concise, high-level overview of the use case. Its purpose is to present the key elements of the project in a clear and accessible manner for business and leadership stakeholders. This section highlights the business context, the problem being addressed, the proposed solution, and the expected value. It also summarises the main outcomes of the analysis or modelling work, along with any recommendations and next steps.
The Executive Summary should enable any reader to quickly understand the essence of the use case, its objectives, and its anticipated impact without requiring them to review the full documentation.
